# ── API URL ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# For running against your LOCAL API server:
#   - Use your machine's local network IP (NOT localhost) so Expo Go on a
#     phone can reach it.  Example: http://192.168.1.100:8080/api
#   - On web/simulator you can use: http://localhost:8080/api
#
# If you leave this empty the app falls back to the deployed production API:
